Make a {lsp}`textDocument/declaration` request.

A request to resolve the type definition locations of a symbol at a given text
document position. The request's parameter is of type <mailto:{@link> TextDocumentPositionParams}
the response is of type <mailto:{@link> Declaration} or a typed array of <mailto:{@link> DeclarationLink}
or a Thenable that resolves to such.

